---
import background from '../assets/background.svg';
---

<div id="container">
	<img id="background" src={background.src} alt="" fetchpriority="high" />
	<main>
		<section id="hero">
			<h1>Automated Coding with AI</h1>
			<p class="tagline">From GitHub issue to pull request, automatically</p>
		</section>

		<section id="workflow">
			<h2>How It Works</h2>

			<p class="workflow-intro">
				Super Shepherd is an automated development workflow that transforms GitHub issues into production-ready code.
				By combining GitHub Actions with Claude Code AI, it eliminates manual coding tasks and accelerates your development cycle.
				Simply label an issue with <code>automated-task</code>, and watch as the entire process‚Äîfrom code generation to pull request creation‚Äîhappens automatically.
				Need changes to a PR? Add a comment with your feedback, then apply the <code>needs-bot-update</code> label to trigger the bot to update the pull request automatically.
			</p>

			<div class="workflow-grid">
				<div class="workflow-step">
					<div class="step-icon">üìù</div>
					<h3>Issue Created</h3>
					<p>Create a GitHub issue with the <code>automated-task</code> label. Describe what you need built or fixed.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="workflow-arrow">‚Üì</div>

				<div class="workflow-step">
					<div class="step-icon">üîç</div>
					<h3>Bot Detects</h3>
					<p>The orchestrator polls every 30 seconds, automatically picking up new labeled issues.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="workflow-arrow">‚Üì</div>

				<div class="workflow-step">
					<div class="step-icon">ü§ñ</div>
					<h3>Claude Codes</h3>
					<p>Claude Code analyzes your repository and autonomously implements the solution.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="workflow-arrow">‚Üì</div>

				<div class="workflow-step">
					<div class="step-icon">‚úÖ</div>
					<h3>PR Created</h3>
					<p>Changes are committed, a pull request is created, and the issue is updated and closed.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</div>

<style>
	#background {
		position: fixed;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		z-index: -1;
		filter: blur(100px);
	}

	#container {
		font-family: Inter, Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', 'Arial Nova', 'Nimbus Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
		min-height: 100vh;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	main {
		width: 100%;
		max-width: 1200px;
		padding: 64px 32px;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 80px;
	}

	#hero {
		text-align: center;
		max-width: 800px;
	}

	h1 {
		font-size: 56px;
		font-weight: 700;
		margin: 0 0 24px 0;
		color: #111827;
		line-height: 1.1;
		background: linear-gradient(83.21deg, #3245ff 0%, #bc52ee 100%);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-clip: text;
	}

	.tagline {
		font-size: 24px;
		color: #4b5563;
		margin: 0;
		line-height: 1.5;
	}

	#workflow {
		width: 100%;
	}

	#workflow h2 {
		text-align: center;
		font-size: 36px;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: #111827;
		margin: 0 0 24px 0;
	}

	.workflow-intro {
		text-align: center;
		font-size: 18px;
		color: #4b5563;
		line-height: 1.7;
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto 48px auto;
		padding: 0 16px;
	}

	.workflow-grid {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 24px;
	}

	.workflow-step {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
		border-radius: 16px;
		padding: 32px 24px;
		width: 100%;
		max-width: 600px;
		text-align: center;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
		transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
		border: 1px solid rgba(50, 69, 255, 0.1);
	}

	.workflow-step:hover {
		transform: translateY(-4px);
		box-shadow: 0 8px 12px rgba(50, 69, 255, 0.15);
	}

	.step-icon {
		font-size: 48px;
		margin-bottom: 16px;
		line-height: 1;
	}

	.workflow-step h3 {
		font-size: 20px;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: #111827;
		margin: 0 0 12px 0;
	}

	.workflow-step p {
		font-size: 14px;
		color: #6b7280;
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.workflow-arrow {
		font-size: 32px;
		color: #3245ff;
		font-weight: 700;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	code {
		display: inline;
		background: rgba(50, 69, 255, 0.1);
		color: #3245ff;
		border-radius: 4px;
		padding: 2px 6px;
		font-size: 13px;
		font-family: ui-monospace, 'Cascadia Code', 'Source Code Pro', Menlo, Consolas, 'DejaVu Sans Mono', monospace;
	}

	@media screen and (max-width: 1024px) {
		h1 {
			font-size: 42px;
		}

		.tagline {
			font-size: 20px;
		}

		#workflow h2 {
			font-size: 30px;
		}

		.workflow-intro {
			font-size: 16px;
		}
	}

	@media screen and (max-width: 640px) {
		main {
			padding: 48px 24px;
			gap: 60px;
		}

		h1 {
			font-size: 36px;
		}

		.tagline {
			font-size: 18px;
		}

		#workflow h2 {
			font-size: 26px;
			margin-bottom: 20px;
		}

		.workflow-intro {
			font-size: 16px;
			margin-bottom: 32px;
		}

		.workflow-step {
			max-width: 400px;
		}
	}
</style>
